chapter:
Welcome to BLFS

The Beyond LinuxFromScratch book is designed to carry on from
where the LFS book leaves off.  Unlike the LFS book, it isn't designed
to be followed straight through.  Reading the  part of this chapter should
help guide you through the book.


Please read most of this part of the book carefully as it explains
quite a few of the conventions we use throughout the book.

